statement.title: Problem Description
statement.content: A range is given, the begin and the end are both integers. You should sum the cube of all the integers in the range.

statement.title: Input
statement.content:
The first line of the input is T(1 <= T <= 1000), which stands for the number of test cases you need to solve.
Each case of input is a pair of integer A,B(0 < A <= B <= 10000),representing the range[A,B].

statement.title: Output
statement.content: For each test case, print a line ��Case #t: ��(without quotes, t means the index of the test case) at the beginning. Then output the answer �C sum the cube of all the integers in the range.
